text: Lady boss Kylie, she is very friendly and helpful, and impressed me with her knowledge of the vacant tables. The stylish decor and excellent drinks create a vibrant atmosphere that effortlessly draws in a lively crowd.

Went there to support my little sister. The place turns out to be quite chilled,with great karaoke and sound systems, spacious and friendly crew/staff. No photos to submit sadly but if I go again I'll remember to update my review. There's also a darts machine there. With roughly around 9 tables in the middle with alot more on the sides. (Smoking room is provided inside)
Nice place for birthday parties and waitress waiter all sing very well and friendly
